OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFresh west to northwest winds
OL,6,Fbringing showers across the area
OL,7,Ftoday. Outbreaks ranging from
OL,8,Foccasional in Dumfries and Galloway to
OL,9,Fisolated in the east, where the best
OL,10,Fof the limited brighter spells appear.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,13,Fa few light showers cropping up. Clear
OL,14,Fspells developing overnight, as the
OL,15,Fshowers largely die out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
