OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FMost enjoying a dry day with
OL,6,Fgood sunny spells and light winds,
OL,7,Fwith the Central Belt particularly
OL,8,Ffavoured and warm. However, sunshine
OL,9,Fincreasingly turning hazy into the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMost
OL,13,Fdry during Monday, with hazy sunshine.
OL,14,FHowever, occasional areas of rain
OL,15,Fcrossing the area from the southwest
OL,16,Ffrom late Monday and through Tuesday
OL,17,Fand Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
